text:
This is an energy switching service. If you complete their switching procedure and don't go ahead, they will fine you £150. No grace period (as required by English law).

http://www.energyhelpline.com/fri/fri/domesticenergy/domestic/getshorthelp?reference=termsandconditions_1

4.7 If a Customer subsequently decides to not proceed with providing its custom to the Supplier in respect of which ENERGYHELPLINE has performed the Price Comparison Service and the Switching Service, ENERGYHELPLINE shall be entitled to charge the Customer an administration fee of £150 plus VAT (the “Contract Cancellation Administration Fee”).
